platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Mettez votre sens tactique à l’épreuve !
An amazing genre mashup that will test your tactics.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Maybe the coolest thing about Crowntakers is how much it feels like a pen-and-paper RPG. From forming a party to saving the king, its mix of exploration and tactical combat is only missing a handful of funky dice. We love the way no two adventures play the same, and how every corner of its world is full of humorous moments.
